      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Amsterdam 18 Decb 1872 ¶ My dear Dr von Müller ¶  ¶ His Majesty the King of the Netherlands ¶ Willem III. ¶  ¶ has expressed his desire to obtain a few specimens of the ¶  ¶ Alsofella's ¶ Alsophila? ¶...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">72.12.18</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From J. H. Ploos van Amstel</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M1,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Library, Royal Botanic Gardens<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Amsterdam 18 Decb 1872</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Dr von Müller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>His Majesty the King of the Netherlands<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Willem III.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has expressed his desire to obtain a few specimens of the</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Alsofella's<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Alsophila?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>or</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Australian ferntree</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Almanac hortocole<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>says — le bon jardinier<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Probably<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Le bon jardinier: Almanach horticole</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Paris).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>first part of the quoted text is in Ardoin (1880),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>p.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>53, under headword 'Alsophile'. A version including the last sentence<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has not been found.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>—</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Très grande fougère arborescente de l'Australie et de l'ile van Diemen s'élèvant à 10 ou 12 mêtres, dont le tronc robuste et quelquefois de 1 mêtre de diametre se termine par une longue touffe de fronds decoupées dont l'ensemble forme une couronne étalée de 15 à 17 mêtres de tour. On n'en possède en Europe que de faibles echantillons, tous apportés directement des lieux de provenance."<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>'Very large arborescent fern of Australia and Van Diemen's island growing to 10 or 12 metres, the trunk of which, robust and sometimes 1 metre in diameter, terminates in a long tuft of separated fronds the whole of which forms a spread crown of 15 to 17 metres around. There are only poor specimens in Europe, all carried directly from their places of origin.'</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Will you kindly grant me your assistance in obtaining the desired plants and your valuable advice respecting the best way of shipping them home. —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I fear there will be many difficulties in the way, as this plant requires much water and shade, however His Majesty is prepared to go to any expense. H. M. desire is to have the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">best</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>specimen of this tree in Europe in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">H. M. gardens</hi>
               </seg>!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I told His Majesty that I should address myself to you, who already had executed so many commissions for H. M. and H. M.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">desired me to express you his thanks for your courtesy and to tell you that the seeds have done exceedingly well</hi>
               </seg>! And so they have done; the gum and wattle tree especially.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My brother Daniel will tell you more about H. M. request, and arrange with you the various matters. —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hoping you will kindly pardon my bold request and accept my sincere thanks for your well known courtesy</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I remain</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your's most sincerely</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J. H. Ploos van Amstel</p>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Alsofella</p>
         </div>
      </body>
